replaced query_listen()
manwe
Mon Apr 21 21:50:16 1997
The function query_listen was obsolete (just an alias for 
query_event(E_MSG))
There is now a new macro in /include/macros.h called LISTEN(object)
This macro has the same functionality as object->query_listen() before.
Please use it, all occurences of query_listen() have been changed.

Manwe
